{"tid":532103,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"咁大個人第一次唔見銀包","createTime":"2018-01-17T13:00:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-02T20:58:33.000Z","uid":76928,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ce593f816fa457448f1613db4adc1435cd957454","tid":532103,"uid":76928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T13:00:40.000Z","msg":"做開CD-ROM嘅我 第一次喺連登po嘢 唔知要開喺咩台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n琴日下午食完嘢之後去咗買嘢都仲喺度<br />\n收埋咗之後 到今日都無用過 直到啱啱想買嘢嗰時 先發現唔見咗<br />\n今朝喺紅磡等車嗰時 覺得俾人撞咗一下個袋<br />\n即刻另轉頭望一望 以為喺有人行過 所以無即刻望下個袋<br />\n所以我根本唔知喺跌咗定俾人偷咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n已經去咗報失 同埋打咗電話去商場同間鋪問<br />\n唔知有無好心人執到/見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/17/203950_3fd70aa0ae1f4f87330412a8b2525443.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F17%2F203950_3fd70aa0ae1f4f87330412a8b2525443.png&h=a767bf9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n喺右下角有波點果隻嚟<br />\n入面有身份證銀行卡嗰啲 仲有幾百蚊喺入面<br />\n如果喺我自己整跌 應該喺沙田和輋附近<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/kurosakimafuyu\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fkurosakimafuyu&d=WGx0PWGxoukb3bVjM6YW8DCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=7807f918\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/kurosakimafuyu</a> 如果有巴絲執到就tg我啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n偷人嘢不得好死!"},{"pid":"2c153a00ee41142353233acc43f963a43c8bd984","tid":532103,"uid":76928,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T13:03:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35a733f640856f8fca18c38d6196a99e8f066a90","tid":532103,"uid":49151,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T13:03:48.000Z","msg"